    "The manipulator consists of 6 interconnected links and rotary joints leading to an end-effector.",
    "Each joint is powered by servomotors that supply the needed torque for link rotation.",
    "This robot is a real-world system used by our industry partner, and we obtained detailed information about it directly from them.",
    "By applying our method to this robot, we aim to assess the efficiency of our approach in a practical case study, capturing the nuances involved in measuring WCET for real-world robotic applications.",
    "This allows us to evaluate the robustness of our method under the specific challenges and constraints present in real-world scenarios."
